Package: eia2
Title: Wrapper for the US Energy Information Administration API Version 2
Version: 0.0.0.9003
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jameel", "Alsalam", email = "jalsalam@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9801-5558")),
    person("Matthew", "Leonawicz", email = "mfleonawicz@gmail.com", role = c("ctb"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9452-2771"))
  )
Description: Provides API access to the open data API from the US Energy
    Information Administration (EIA) <https://www.eia.gov/opendata/>. Use of the
    API requires a free API key. The package includes functions to request data
    using API parameters including data columns, facets, start and end dates, 
    and sorting. The version 2 API provides a compatibility endpoint for 
    retrieving data using version 1 API series ID's.
